INSTALL
=======

git clone git@github.com:djm/dotfiles.git ~/dotfiles/

Bash Config
-----------

ln -s ~/dotfiles/bash/{linux|macosx}.bashrc ~/.bashrc
ln -s ~/dotfiles/bash/.inputrc ~/.inputrc

Git Config
----------

ln -s ~/dotfiles/git/.gitconfig ~/.gitconfig
ln -s ~/dotfiles/git/.gitignore ~/.gitignore

Mercurial Config
----------------
ln -s ~/dotfiles/hg/.hgext ~/.hgext
# We copy instead of link as we tend to store auth details in hgrc.
cp ~/dotfiles/hg/.hgrc ~/.hgrc

Vim Config
----------

ln -s ~/dotfiles/vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
ln -s ~/dotfiles/vim/.vim/ ~/.vim

RadioTray Bookmarks
-------------------

ln -s ~/dotfiles/radiotray/bookmarks.xml ~/.local/share/radiotray/bookmarks.xml
